                  </hi>. I am a policeman. The prosecutor informed me of his loss, I accompanied him to the prisoner's mother's, and asked the prisoner about the spoons—she denied all knowledge of it—I found a piece of new net in her pocket—I took her to the pawnbroker's, and they recognised her as having pawned the two spoons—when she came out, she acknowledged having pawned different spoons, and told me where she had</p>
